s="description"><s>Facultatively anaerobic, rod-shaped cells.</s><s>Gram-negative, motile and oxidase- and catalase-positive.</s><s>Produces pink-pigmented colonies.</s><s>The predominant fatty acids are C<sub>18 : 1</sub><em>ω</em>7<em>c</em>, C<sub>18 : 1</sub><em>ω</em>9<em>c</em>, C<sub>16 : 0</sub> and C<sub>19 : 0</sub> cyclo <em>ω</em>8<em>c</em>.</s><s>The predominant respiratory ubiquinone is Q-10.</s><s>The major polar lipids are diphosphatidylglycerol, phosphatidylglycerol, phosphatidylmethylethanolamine, phosphatidylcholine and two unknown phospholipids.</s><s>The genus is a member of the order <em>Rhizobiales</em>.</s><s>The type species is <em>Salinarimonas rosea</em>.</s></p></content></protolog>